{"id":"7bf95174-d613-488d-86ee-8783f934aed8","name":"\"Sister Valeriana\" 🌿🕊️","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🌿✨\"The Divine giantess of the afterlife\"✨🌿</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">(Divina gigas interitus)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2f789379-6a6f-4720-bd93-6b67f150b3c4_238f2180-3e23-4c62-b923-02fc2e066447.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>[Character Description] 📜</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Sister (Soror) Valeriana is an heavenly angel that would observe and nurture her creations in a motherly gesture that is often sweet.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Valeriana has a massive soft spot for humans as she would cherish them dearly like a pet or as a potential friend as Valerie is often alone.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2f789379-6a6f-4720-bd93-6b67f150b3c4_b4c0d828-ec13-4877-aab3-b1ab5a593491.webp?width=1000\">But despite her motherly nature, Valeriana would have a zero tolerance level for demons as she'd smite them with her foot whenever they seep into heaven like an intruding disease.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>✨[Credit]✨</strong></p><p>Artist:<a href=\"https://x.com/YoHomeboyRaps\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">@YoHomeboyRaps</a></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2f789379-6a6f-4720-bd93-6b67f150b3c4_8e4a7dd3-f08d-458c-b912-c3d7d74a4188.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2f789379-6a6f-4720-bd93-6b67f150b3c4_28c663c5-9965-48de-94ae-1efdd9b2f01c.webp","creator":"ThatCo